<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="f9021af2-4d1d-45e6-9a6c-13f3e47702b3"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="e3740e1a-3f56-4793-a8da-7b015d32360f">Damage Vulnerabilities</span>&nbsp;bludgeoning</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="86c86841-3423-4a0c-a82f-b1eb4adfc49e"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="0beb3cdb-1e58-4d53-b719-1550f4e9e313">Damage Immunit</span><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="8725ed75-4fb4-4a37-9598-afb93145759f">ies</span>&nbsp;poison</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="0c4cd885-5e69-4693-b0bc-7cfd87ace9dc"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="d9dd725f-0efb-437d-85c2-ef2e51619d99">Condition Immunities</span>&nbsp;<a class="tooltip-hover condition-tooltip" href="/compendium/rules/basic-rules/appendix-a-conditions#Exhaustion" data-tooltip-href="/conditions/4-tooltip">exhaustion</a>, <a class="tooltip-hover condition-tooltip" href="/compendium/rules/basic-rules/appendix-a-conditions#Poisoned" data-tooltip-href="/conditions/11-tooltip">poisoned</a></p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="3da2223b-3391-4e6f-8e80-4f2d51729308"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="db41c4c4-e79e-4a03-9124-4f7248a2afa2">Senses</span>&nbsp;<a class="tooltip-hover sense-tooltip" href="/compendium/rules/basic-rules/monsters#Darkvision" data-tooltip-href="/senses/2-tooltip">darkvision</a> 60 ft., passive Perception 9</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="efcefce9-a2c6-4b4e-96ba-c60218335ba1"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="e2b01bea-8281-4ce2-b21f-1afa683c4646">L</span><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="4c998d5d-4624-4ea9-a9d1-1e2d72f4891c">anguages</span>&nbsp;—</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data-Last" data-content-chunk-id="cffa9d44-c0f6-46ce-a761-47d5728fbbc4"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="5afd79ad-763b-485a-93bd-ebaca475ef0e">Challenge</span>&nbsp;1/2 (100 XP)</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Heading--after-last-bar-" data-content-chunk-id="bf76e6f8-15f9-4152-82aa-1eee614e0015">Actions</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Body" data-content-chunk-id="28e0bdb4-e0d9-4cd1-ab2f-b9243af744aa"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Inline-Subhead-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="f416d57a-e10f-4a97-90e7-90d46020add0">Hooves.&nbsp;</span><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Italic-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="a2695030-b11f-46fb-85fa-3f0781d006e5">Melee Weapon Attack:</span>&nbsp;+6 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target.&nbsp;<span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Italic-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="0faea551-c882-4e05-9c60-450a2c4ae896">Hit:</span>&nbsp;11 (2d6 + 4) bludgeoning damage.</p>
