<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="cc1abf56-7748-4b64-9021-54afa40aa5d8"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="5c27306f-5c4b-432c-a60b-a042a1030830">Armor</span>&nbsp;Class 14 (natural armor)</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="7f35a2d1-c8da-47a4-b0cc-0f161dd8148e"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="6950ad32-4e0c-4bc6-801a-2c0e0af93b60">Hit Points</span>&nbsp;114 (12d10 + 48)</p>
