<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Metadata" data-content-chunk-id="fb142960-d1c7-4aea-81f5-74d685b26133">Tiny beast, unaligned</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="4cadaee2-6773-452f-9a50-6b86f4579f75"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="5ade77bc-77f1-4c09-addd-a86deba03e46">Armo</span><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="0c70a076-0241-4cec-83b3-c3f0da481b07">r Class</span>&nbsp;13</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="c6658ccc-c074-4bda-955f-e4cb43a9be90"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="4521031c-8d08-4508-8e1e-4c86fd476482">Hit Points</span>&nbsp;1 (1d4 − 1)</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="134c422b-cc44-481e-8d97-dd1c0f0f52d2"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="abb0baac-903c-4146-a8ca-8187d5ee001d">Sp</span><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="2be268ae-c72d-4e20-9352-6c4889e02279">eed</span>&nbsp;30 ft.</p>
