<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="effd7432-09ac-4694-aac9-496b3c75ce78"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="65dc8a2c-6a03-4d2a-a3da-39b0ba77f2f9">Hit Points</span>&nbsp;32 (5d8 + 10)</p>
