<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Heading--after-last-bar-" data-content-chunk-id="107ac5aa-7b61-4486-b4c0-f4ffa4a1490b">Actions</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Body" data-content-chunk-id="f3a12a24-8496-4590-a430-613622eb2dcb"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Inline-Subhead-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="8a61523f-ec9c-4cb3-b9a9-f8265f7c85ef">Bite</span><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Inline-Subhead-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="b3ffe316-72a7-44d4-b406-dc20483115b3">.&nbsp;</span><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Italic-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="854801f8-da0c-4b79-8518-32555ecd3375">Melee Weapon Attack:</span>&nbsp;+4 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target.&nbsp;<span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Italic-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="b4eeee2e-f677-449d-b34e-9d3979030b5b">Hit:</span>&nbsp;7 (1d10 + 2) piercing damage plus 2 (1d4) cold damage.</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Body" data-content-chunk-id="c83784ca-dba1-47fa-ab09-b64827f5a638"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Inline-Subhead-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="a9ddecfc-b110-4f17-a395-778cb237693f">Cold Breath (Recharge 5–6).&nbsp;</span>The dragon exhales an icy blast of hail in a 15-foot cone. Each creature in that area must make a DC 12 Constitution saving throw, taking 22 (5d8) cold damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.</p>
