<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="138e2f72-48de-41eb-8783-be034212884c"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="639c9580-2028-415c-aab2-f002e896639f">Skills</span>&nbsp;<a class="tooltip-hover skill-tooltip" href="/compendium/rules/basic-rules/using-ability-scores#Perception" data-tooltip-href="/skills/14-tooltip">Perception</a> +5, <a class="tooltip-hover skill-tooltip" href="/compendium/rules/basic-rules/using-ability-scores#Stealth" data-tooltip-href="/skills/5-tooltip">Stealth</a> +3</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="898818e2-44f9-4e2f-8ade-1943844d0d66"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="3e4f02c1-d1ce-4c6e-b039-2c9c91c44428">Damage Immun</span><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="afff7aee-0811-40d8-9dc9-1356c17f4e1f">ities&nbsp;</span>cold</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="91982b55-08bc-412b-9eac-b07aa1520065"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="ff8a2199-c218-4462-9008-d9c06c6f8c96">Senses</span>&nbsp;passive Perception 15</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="474b599b-b4cc-44ce-b359-c21ff47078af"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="10b10918-b039-4791-8404-5e08993dbcc2">Languages</span>&nbsp;Common, Giant, Winter Wolf</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data-Last" data-content-chunk-id="76d6696d-3ea0-4277-940b-494cdc34ad32"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="e48ecc64-93ac-4a0a-82ea-522ff79387cb">Challenge&nbsp;</span>3 (700 XP)</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Body" data-content-chunk-id="14648184-b0f2-4dae-854d-a1207d523f8a"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Inline-Subhead-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="c5f02b54-c52f-4dd5-8cc6-c63f2c490da4">Keen Hearing and Smell.</span>&nbsp;The wolf has advantage on Wisdom (<a class="tooltip-hover skill-tooltip" href="/compendium/rules/basic-rules/using-ability-scores#Perception" data-tooltip-href="/skills/14-tooltip">Perception</a>) checks that rely on hearing or smell.</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Body" data-content-chunk-id="f0f8ca3e-cbfa-4dd4-a932-fe1852a81386"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Inline-Subhead-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="2ecd8670-6270-45f5-81bf-1f5d6a8f79c4">Pack Tactics.&nbsp;</span>The wolf has advantage on an attack roll against a creature if at least one of the wolf’s allies is within 5 feet of the creature and the ally isn’t <a class="tooltip-hover condition-tooltip" href="/compendium/rules/basic-rules/appendix-a-conditions#Incapacitated" data-tooltip-href="/conditions/7-tooltip">incapacitated</a>.</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Body-Last--apply-before-heading-" data-content-chunk-id="31193315-75d5-4f69-9632-02c355d10dc9"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Inline-Subhead-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="2708700c-4c47-40af-a12b-6904d553715c">Snow Camouflage.&nbsp;</span>The wolf has advantage on Dexterity (<a class="tooltip-hover skill-tooltip" href="/compendium/rules/basic-rules/using-ability-scores#Stealth" data-tooltip-href="/skills/5-tooltip">Stealth</a>) checks made to hide in snowy terrain.</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Heading" data-content-chunk-id="bf4e955e-6775-4380-aa3b-88a1da1733c1">Actions</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Body" data-content-chunk-id="6979efca-b118-4547-8e6b-57d0c9038737"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Inline-Subhead-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="626072a5-0bcb-45f5-95b9-8fb406ca3e6f">Bite.</span>&nbsp;<span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Italic-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="2a356309-1c67-4ad9-a6c4-bf5419f85fac">Melee Weapon Attack:</span>&nbsp;+6 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target.&nbsp;<span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Italic-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="418b86db-927d-4cb1-b61c-6c73cd1051e9">Hit:&nbsp;</span>11 (2d6 + 4) piercing damage. If the target is a creature, it must succeed on a DC 14 Strength saving throw or be knocked <a class="tooltip-hover condition-tooltip" href="/compendium/rules/basic-rules/appendix-a-conditions#Prone" data-tooltip-href="/conditions/12-tooltip">prone</a>.</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Body" data-content-chunk-id="734bb578-1fc0-4f98-a886-b189da42d795"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Inline-Subhead-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="6792f944-3871-43c2-8afe-be3d1f430bbb">Cold Breath (Recharge 5–6).</span>&nbsp;The wolf exhales a blast of freezing wind in a 15-foot cone. Each creature in that area must make a DC 12 Dexterity saving throw, taking 18 (4d8) cold damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.</p>
</div>
<p class="Core-Styles_Core-Body" data-content-chunk-id="daf58043-146a-4bfd-b350-f5182bed4d2f">Arctic-dwelling winter wolves are evil and intelligent creatures with snow-white fur and pale blue eyes.</p>
