<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="22ca75a6-fae5-4db8-bad1-409caaf7b870"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="817ec80b-243d-44b5-8648-fad2d9c6aff6">Senses</span>&nbsp;<a class="tooltip-hover sense-tooltip" href="/compendium/rules/basic-rules/monsters#Darkvision" data-tooltip-href="/senses/2-tooltip">darkvision</a> 60 ft., passive Perception 14</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="0aa74d73-4dec-43d8-98b8-6b61565ea32c"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="6fbf1950-a452-4918-8ef0-75eb5668cbe7">Languages</span>&nbsp;Goblin, Worg</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data-Last" data-content-chunk-id="aced4d62-439b-41f6-9b65-39c054a6e38e"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="6e301020-9244-45b1-b5db-49298fe43102">Challenge&nbsp;</span>1/2 (100 XP)</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Body-Last--apply-before-heading-" data-content-chunk-id="414a4447-9f18-495f-9f83-a4bb0c6dbc32"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Inline-Subhead-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="1f84d0ec-308d-4874-90ef-f20798bce913">Keen Hearing and Smell.</span>&nbsp;The worg has advantage on Wisdom (<a class="tooltip-hover skill-tooltip" href="/compendium/rules/basic-rules/using-ability-scores#Perception" data-tooltip-href="/skills/14-tooltip">Perception</a>) checks that rely on hearing or smell.</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Heading" data-content-chunk-id="1a3407cd-f28f-4f06-ba75-9f38b0740c6e">Actions</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Body" data-content-chunk-id="894d0404-8df8-426b-ac1d-610fe9c58716"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Inline-Subhead-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="0d4aaa93-f738-47a3-a3c6-11b89b62ddd7">Bite.</span>&nbsp;<span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Italic-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="49610222-7ca3-4670-b895-2db798a840e4">Melee Weapon Attack:</span>&nbsp;+5 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target.&nbsp;<span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Italic-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="c9442200-9849-406f-885b-201cc506dec4">Hit:&nbsp;</span>10 (2d6 + 3) piercing damage. If the target is a creature, it must succeed on a DC 13 Strength saving throw or be knocked <a class="tooltip-hover condition-tooltip" href="/compendium/rules/basic-rules/appendix-a-conditions#Prone" data-tooltip-href="/conditions/12-tooltip">prone</a>.</p>
