<p class="Core-Styles_Core-Body" data-content-chunk-id="8e507c35-eb84-4c5c-bfbd-9ac78a36e6ef">A worg is a monstrous wolf-like predator that delights in hunting and devouring creatures weaker than itself.</p>
<div id="_idContainer047" class="Basic-Text-Frame" data-content-chunk-id="69e21b12-bec3-4693-af66-8a8ce311f3e2">
